Vice President expresses his admiration for Senator Chris Dodd, describing him as a close friend and one of the most skilled legislators he has worked with. He praises Dodd's intelligence, expertise in foreign policy, and his contributions to important issues such as health reform and economic stability. The Vice President believes that Dodd's legacy will be recognized as significant and highlights his dedication to protecting the welfare of children. He expresses confidence that Dodd will continue to be a source of advice and counsel, and wishes him and his wife the best in their future endeavors.